$interpreted: Old Bear Priest: Down this path is Golem Totem Cave. The chieftain and I will be waiting here.
Old Bear Priest: Return to us once you've completed your Rite of Passage.
Old Bear Priest: ...*growl*...RARGH!!
Teenage Bear: ...*growl*...*growl*...!
Crushfang: Dagger...
Dagger: What would it feel like...
Furygrowl: What are you talking about?
Dagger: I mean these dying Golems. I wonder what it feels like walking towards death?
Furygrowl: It's probably quite tranquil, being able to die peacefully in their sanctuary.
Dagger: Never thought our path to adulthood would be the same as the Golems' path to the afterlife.
Dagger: You're a good fighter. After the Rite of Passage, wanna join our little operation?
Furygrowl: What operation?
Dagger: An attack on the Sunshine Infantry.
Furygrowl: Huh? Does the chieftain know of this?
Dagger: No way, that coward only knows how to say no. My father died covering his hairy butt!
Dagger: Totally not worth it!
Furygrowl: The chieftain is no coward, at least not to me. My brother once got caught in one of the humans' traps.
Furygrowl: If it weren't for the chieftain, my brother would have been dead meat.
Dagger: The chieftain saved your brother?
? ? ?: Help! I can't hold out much longer!
Dagger: Someone needs help!
Furygrowl: I heard it too... let's check it out!
Dagger: Why is it so quiet?
Furygrowl: Victory, or utter defeat?
Furygrowl: Look out!
Dagger: Now that was a good fight!
Furygrowl: Helmetal Pinchers rarely leave their natural habitat. Did someone bait it out?
Dagger: Maybe someone bored of fighting all those wimpy humans!
Furygrowl: By the way, the cave we're looking for should be nearby. We'll get our fate weapons there.
Dagger: Let's split up, find our weapons, then head back to the chieftain and finish our Rite of Passage.
Furygrowl: Alright, good luck!
Dagger: Pesky little things.
Dagger: Ha, I choose you.
Dagger: What the heck is this thing? A fish!?

Furygrowl: Bwahahaha~ sorry... hahaha~
That doesn't suit you at all! Bwahaha~!
Dagger: You better stop laughing if you know what's good for ya!
Furygrowl: Bwaha~ Or what? You gonna fish slap me!?

Furygrowl: Hahaha~
Hold on...! Where are you going!?
Dagger: Getting another weapon.
Furygrowl: Rules are rules. Once you've made your choice, there's no backsies.
Dagger: No one will know as long as you keep your mouth shut.
Furygrowl: I don't know if I can do that! This is way too funny~!
Old Bear Priest: Ah, the first group to clear the Rite of Passage is here. Not bad. Not bad, indeed. You're the fastest group in recent years.
Crushfang: Dagger, I congratulate you in place of your father, Razorclaw.
Crushfang: As a grown bear, I will no longer restrict you. You are now responsible for your own actions.
Dagger: Hmph!
